{"compressionlevel":-1,"height":35,"infinite":false,"layers":[{"draworder":"topdown","id":8,"name":"SemanticZones","objects":[{"height":42,"id":2,"name":"中华小面馆(China Noodle Restaurant)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这是一家中华传统小面馆，有中国各种面食。包括兰州牛肉拉面、杂酱面、重庆小面、油泼面等。在这里可以吃饱喝足，恢复饥饿。\n(This is a traditional Chinese noodle restaurant featuring various types of Chinese noodles. Including Lanzhou beef noodles, mutton and bean paste noodles, Chongqing small noodles, and oil-spiked noodles, etc. Here, you can eat and drink to your heart's content and regain your strength.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":43,"x":354,"y":115},{"height":45,"id":3,"name":"旅馆 (The Prancing Pony Inn)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这是一家温暖的木制旅馆，角落里有壁炉，可以用来休息和打听情报。\n(This is a cozy wooden inn. There is a fireplace in the corner, which can be used for resting and gathering information.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":62,"x":257,"y":112},{"height":44,"id":5,"name":"武器防具店(Weapon and Armor Store)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这是一家武器防具店，在这里可以购买各类剑、法杖、枪、刀、投掷类等武器，以及盾、护甲等防具。\n(This is a weapons and armors store. Here, you can purchase various types of swords, wands, guns, knives, throwing weapons, as well as shields and armor for protection.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":63,"x":160,"y":211},{"height":44,"id":6,"name":"魔法药水店(Magic Potion Shop)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"可以购买各类魔法药水，包括恢复类、增益类和负面攻击类药水。同时也可以找店内女巫进行占卜。\n(You can purchase various types of magic potions, including those for healing, enhancing, and dealing negative damage. At the same time, you can also consult the witch in the store for a divination.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":44,"x":259,"y":210},{"height":68,"id":7,"name":"练习场（Practice Ground）","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这里是练习场，可以在这里锻炼，并磨练能力，也可以找人切磋。\n(This is the practice field. You can exercise here, hone your skills, and also compete with others.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":103,"x":365,"y":238},{"height":67,"id":8,"name":"仓库(Warehouse)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这里是仓库，存储了各类物资。\n(This place stores various kinds of supplies.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"building","visible":true,"width":61,"x":354,"y":14},{"height":41,"id":9,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":44,"x":2,"y":52},{"height":43,"id":10,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":37,"x":149,"y":36},{"height":40,"id":11,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":35,"x":39,"y":245},{"height":33,"id":12,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":43,"x":3,"y":178},{"height":23,"id":13,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":27,"x":51,"y":210},{"height":25,"id":14,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":26,"x":323,"y":261},{"height":14,"id":15,"name":"树(Tree)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"一棵树，可以乘凉。\n(A tree can provide shade.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":18,"x":220,"y":110},{"height":13,"id":16,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"石板路(Paved road)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":315,"x":163,"y":163},{"height":158,"id":17,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"石板路(Paved road)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":13,"x":450,"y":3},{"height":0,"id":19,"name":"池塘(Pond)","opacity":1,"polygon":[{"x":0,"y":0},{"x":14,"y":-1},{"x":17,"y":12},{"x":16,"y":32},{"x":9,"y":39},{"x":-4,"y":38},{"x":-10,"y":23},{"x":-10,"y":5},{"x":-9,"y":-3}],"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这是池塘，里面有鱼，可以闲着无聊看看鱼。\n(This is a pond. There are fish in it. You can just sit there and watch the fish if you are bored.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":0,"x":115,"y":254},{"height":0,"id":20,"name":"池塘(Pond)","opacity":1,"polygon":[{"x":0,"y":0},{"x":11,"y":0},{"x":17,"y":6},{"x":22,"y":22},{"x":18,"y":35},{"x":5,"y":41},{"x":1,"y":39}],"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"这是更大的池塘，里面有一些睡莲，据说这个池塘通往更大的湖泊，有更外面的世界。\n(This is a larger pond, with some water lilies in it. It is said that this pond leads to a larger lake, to the outside world.)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":0,"x":1,"y":221},{"height":11,"id":22,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"石板路(Paved road)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":170,"x":147,"y":258},{"height":42,"id":23,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"石板路(Paved road)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":17,"x":400,"y":178},{"height":42,"id":24,"name":"草丛(Grassland)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"草丛(Grassland)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"nature","visible":true,"width":43,"x":98,"y":195},{"height":79,"id":25,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"石板路(Paved road)"}],"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":14,"x":223,"y":176},{"height":76,"id":27,"name":"石板路(Paved road)","opacity":1,"rotation":0,"type":"floor","visible":true,"width":13,"x":337,"y":177},{"name":"图书馆(Library)","type":"building","x":512,"y":50,"width":70,"height":55,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"安静的小镇图书馆，藏有珍贵的古籍与地图。(A quiet town library with precious ancient texts and maps.)"}],"id":28},{"name":"神社(Shrine)","type":"building","x":530,"y":200,"width":60,"height":50,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"古老的神社，供奉着守护小镇的神灵。许愿池旁立着石灯笼。(An ancient shrine dedicated to the town guardian spirit. Stone lanterns beside a wishing well.)"}],"id":29},{"name":"农场(Farm)","type":"nature","x":200,"y":350,"width":120,"height":80,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"金黄的麦田和菜园，农夫正在辛勤劳作。(Golden wheat fields and vegetable gardens. Farmers work diligently.)"}],"id":30},{"name":"铁匠铺(Blacksmith)","type":"building","x":640,"y":130,"width":55,"height":50,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"铁匠的工坊，炉火通明，叮叮当当的锤击声不绝于耳。(The blacksmith forge glows bright, the clang of hammer on anvil never ceases.)"}],"id":31},{"name":"码头(Fishing Dock)","type":"nature","x":50,"y":380,"width":80,"height":50,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"小镇南边的木码头，几条小船停泊在岸边，是钓鱼的好地方。(A wooden dock on the south side of town. Small boats are moored nearby — a great fishing spot.)"}],"id":32},{"name":"花园(Garden)","type":"nature","x":510,"y":320,"width":90,"height":70,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"精心打理的花园，各种奇花异草争奇斗艳，蝴蝶翩翩起舞。(A meticulously tended garden with exotic flowers. Butterflies dance among the blossoms.)"}],"id":33},{"name":"瞭望塔(Watchtower)","type":"building","x":650,"y":20,"width":40,"height":60,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"高耸的石头瞭望塔，可以俯瞰整个小镇和远方的山脉。(A tall stone watchtower overlooking the entire town and distant mountains.)"}],"id":34},{"name":"温泉(Hot Springs)","type":"nature","x":620,"y":350,"width":70,"height":60,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"天然温泉池，水面升腾着白色蒸汽，令人放松身心。(Natural hot spring pools with white steam rising — deeply relaxing.)"}],"id":35},{"name":"集市(Marketplace)","type":"building","x":350,"y":350,"width":100,"height":60,"properties":[{"name":"description","type":"string","value":"热闹的露天集市，各种摊位售卖着稀奇古怪的商品。(A bustling open-air market with stalls selling all manner of curious goods.)"}],"id":36},{"name":"树(Tree)","type":"nature","x":500,"y":140,"width":30,"height":35,"id":37},{"name":"树(Tree)","type":"nature","x":700,"y":260,"width":25,"height":30,"id":38},{"name":"树(Tree)","type":"nature","x":580,"y":420,"width":30,"height":35,"id":39},{"name":"草丛(Grassland)","type":"nature","x":450,"y":400,"width":60,"height":50,"id":40},{"name":"草丛(Grassland)","type":"nature","x":680,"y":70,"width":50,"height":40,"id":41},{"name":"石板路(Paved road)","type":"floor","x":465,"y":163,"width":340,"height":13,"id":42},{"name":"石板路(Paved road)","type":"floor","x":560,"y":176,"width":13,"height":270,"id":43}],"opacity":1,"type":"objectgroup","visible":true,"x":0,"y":0},{"data":[266,266,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,26,265,68,111,178,178,111,68,97,68,26,97,111,68,111,178,111,178,178,97,97,68,266,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,287,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,26,265,111,97,26,265,26,26,97,111,26,178,265,26,265,97,68,97,111,178,178,68,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,265,268,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,111,26,265,111,68,111,111,68,111,97,97,97,265,265,178,265,26,178,265,111,26,111,68,265,265,265,265,265,159,160,162,265,265,265,265,155,289,111,111,111